People don't come here and post about quests to be dorked around by people looking to inflate their ego by lording information over others.  People come here to collaborate, because it's fun to work stuff out with other people instead of beating your head on the wall solo.  They do it here because the tools for communication ingame literally suck.  People also come here (or to other 'spoiler' sites) because they are completely frustrated and stuck on a quest, and would give up completely on it, if not for an answer to a question or two.  There's not any good way to get this information across without the ability for them to go ahead and read the whole thing, but hey, that's their choice.<br>
<br>
